It was a dark and stormy night; the month was October; the year was 2020 as the ever diligent writefag continued to type out frantic sentences for his new green. The lightning and the thunder distracting him from his continued devotion stories about fuzzy whamen. His eyes dart to his browser—A new thread! A reset from shitposting, a new chance to talk about the wonders of his favorite waifur, an opportunity to have a new favorite. But to the Writefag, it was a time of fear. Who! Who had posted new stories? His eyes glance over the same people—Yes! Thank God, no one he couldn’t compete with them. No sight of a Kitsune Update. No Velociraptors today! The Senorita is down, down, down on the list. The fabled Roo’d Apocalypse isn’t upon us. The Writefag does a little jig amidst the downpour outside. No one can ruin him.

Then his blood run colds, at the very top! There is a new story, not an update, but brand new! Missed because the OP messed up the formatting. That title? What does that even mean?
